data.description: Welcome to 5402 Fruitwood Dr, Louisville, Kentucky 40272! This stunning property sits on a spacious .33-acre corner lot, providing ample space and privacy. As you approach the home, you'll notice a wide driveway leading to a 3-car garage, offering plenty of parking and storage options. One of the highlights of this property is the refreshing pool, complete with a brand new liner. Imagine enjoying summer days lounging by the pool or hosting memorable pool parties with family and friends. Inside the house, you'll find a fresh coat of paint throughout, creating a clean and inviting atmosphere. The appliances in the home will also stay with the property, making it convenient for the new owners to settle in and start enjoying their new home! See Agent Notes!
